Package: libbc-io-dev
Source: libbc-io
Version: 1.1.0-1
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Younes Benmoussa <younes.benmoussa@pm.me>
Installed-Size: 67
Depends: libbc-core-dev (>= 1.3.0), libbc-allocators-dev (>= 1.2.0)
Section: libdevel
Priority: optional
Multi-Arch: same
Homepage: https://unmanaged-bytes.com/
Description: bc-* ecosystem I/O primitives (development files)
 Open/close file wrappers, path and inode helpers, mmap, and a
 buffered stream with explicit advise hints. Thin Linux-specific
 layer above libc syscalls.
 .
 This package ships the static library, public headers, and
 pkg-config descriptor required to build against bc-io.
